{"type": "article", "id": 27500, "title": "手扶椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110301VZ8c2RBK5GhsFzai.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>我们之前曾经介绍过加拿大设计师 Philippe Malouin 设计的一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27290.html\">日食壁灯</a>，这次他延续了自己一贯的简约风格，为 <a href=\"http://establishedandsons.com/\">Established and Sons</a> 设计了名为 <a href=\"http://philippemalouin.com/new-gallery-1/\">Mollo</a> 的扶手椅。圆鼓鼓的 Mollo 外型非常简单，内部柔软的泡沫材料会让人深陷其中，很适合坐下小憩。目前，这款手扶椅仅能在 Established and Sons 的专卖店购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110300b3B02uiyTNsr18lM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.78515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110300nQEbm5dDVsu3iUkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110301BFVfbNym5xMU3ZIC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}